### **User Stories (Travelers)**

1. **Account & Authentication**  
   * As a **new user**, I want to **sign up with email/password** so that I can **save my trips and preferences**.  
   * As a **registered user**, I want to **log in to my account** so that I can **access my saved trips and profile**.  
   * As a **user**, I want to **reset my password via email** so that I can **recover my account if I forget my credentials**.  
2. **Trip Planning**  
   * As a **user**, I want to **create a new trip by entering destination, dates, and activities** so that I can **get personalized recommendations**.  
   * As a **user**, I want to **view a list of my saved trips** so that I can **easily revisit my plans**.  
   * As a **user**, I want to **edit or delete a saved trip** so that I can **update my travel details**.  
3. **Weather & Outfit Recommendations**  
   * As a **user**, I want to **see real-time weather forecasts for my destination** (via OpenWeather API) so that I can **pack appropriately**.  
   * As a **user**, I want to **get outfit suggestions based on weather, season, and activities** so that I can **dress comfortably**.  
   * As a **user**, I want to **customize outfit recommendations by adding/removing items** so that I can **tailor them to my style**.  
4. **Packing Lists**  
   * As a **user**, I want to **auto-generate a packing list based on trip duration, weather, and activities** (via PackPoint API) so that I **donâ€™t forget essentials**.  
   * As a **user**, I want to **manually add/remove items from my packing list** so that I can **include personal items**.  
   * As a **user**, I want to **mark items as packed/unpacked** so that I can **track my progress**.  
5. **Travel Tips & Local Insights**  
   * As a **user**, I want to **view cultural dress codes and local customs for my destination** (e.g., via OpenAI suggestions) so that I can **respect traditions**.  
   * As a **user**, I want to **see must-have travel items for my destination** (e.g., adapters, vaccines) so that I can **prepare thoroughly**.

---

### **Admin Stories (Backend Management)**

6. **Content & API Management**  
   * As an **admin**, I want to **manage API integrations (OpenWeather, PackPoint, etc.)** so that I can **ensure data accuracy**.  
   * As an **admin**, I want to **update travel tips and cultural guidelines manually** so that I can **provide reliable advice**.  
7. **User & Data Oversight**  
   * As an **admin**, I want to **view and delete user accounts** so that I can **handle misuse or inactive users**.  
   * As an **admin**, I want to **monitor trip statistics (popular destinations, frequent users)** so that I can **improve recommendations**.  
8. **System Maintenance**  
   * As an **admin**, I want to **receive alerts for API failures** (e.g., weather service downtime) so that I can **resolve issues quickly**.  
   * As an **admin**, I want to **backup user data regularly** so that I can **prevent data loss**.

---

### **Key Technical Considerations for Your Team**

* **APIs Needed**: OpenWeather (weather), PackPoint (packing lists), Google Places (destination info), OpenAI (cultural tips).  
* **Django Features**: User auth, database models for trips/packing lists, API integrations, responsive templates.  
* **Team**: Split work into auth (1 person), APIs (2 people), UI (1 person), testing/deployment (1 person).
